### Create Product (multipart/form-data)
POST http://localhost:3000/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category"

BAG
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="modelCode"

CHN-010
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Bolsa Teste
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Bolsa de teste para validar o endpoint de criação de produtos.
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="material"

Couro Sintético
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="size"

MEDIUM
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

299.90
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="isPromotion"

true
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="promotionPrice"

249.90
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="colors"

[{"colorName":"Preto","hexCode":"#000000","stockQuantity":25},{"colorName":"Vermelho","hexCode":"#C41E3A","stockQuantity":15}]
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="colors[0][images]"; filename="bolsa_preto_frente.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-images/sample1.jpg
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="colors[0][images]"; filename="bolsa_preto_lateral.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-images/sample2.jpg
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="colors[1][images]"; filename="bolsa_vermelho_frente.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-images/sample3.jpg
------FormBoundary--

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:3000/products HTTP/1.1

### Get Product By ID
GET http://localhost:3000/products/{{productId}} HTTP/1.1
